{"tid":1676400,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"病真係好撚辛苦 有冇人明","createTime":"2019-10-26T12:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T04:51:57.000Z","uid":198607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fdbcd3c679edbdeb65cf0cae6b251b2b2df5f853","tid":1676400,"uid":198607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:14:24.000Z","msg":"8月到而家總共病咗6,7次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />次次好返完好快又病<br />\n而家咳到好撚想割咗喉嚨佢<br />\n<br />\n究竟點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢兩個月都有做運動 日日食菜食水果 好鍾意飲水 瞓覺唔開冷氣 無飲凍野<br />\n我已經算係會保持健康習慣喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解身體都係咁差 我而家已經驚緊今次病完 好快又會再病 究竟我可以點 求連登醫師解答"},{"pid":"86d758e5b9f3a55ede8e3050d6f498b3d55807d1","tid":1676400,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:15:21.000Z","msg":"長期病仲辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5bbd2755348dc903a89d2de27a9c47e7001027c","tid":1676400,"uid":198607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:17:31.000Z","msg":"講起唔開冷氣 我呢一兩年慣咗 以前一定要開到24度 而家越嚟越弱 一定唔可以開 有時喺廳到屋企人要開 我都一定要開到成27 28度（都要著件褸著長褲）但佢地係覺得熱<br />\n今年仲好後生 但身體機能已經去到70歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a80f5904a08856f4ac205baa8f6ed550a4c5980","tid":1676400,"uid":198607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86d758e5b9f3a55ede8e3050d6f498b3d55807d1","tid":1676400,"uid":250511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:15:21.000Z","msg":"長期病仲辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />絲打頂住"},{"pid":"f10403f55aa8237a90be942bee54d1ec6d713615","tid":1676400,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食維他命c咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你on9定真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abc4ef95faadf67c0a58474a8bd391c82ce8c6a","tid":1676400,"uid":7169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:29:58.000Z","msg":"幾多碎？<br />\n瞓覺個陣喉嚨痛真係想死 口水都唔敢吞<br />\n試下食幸福剋咳素 喉嚨㾗個隻咳好有效"},{"pid":"744d9e886b1f04235225f1a5366e5d68c2f16deb","tid":1676400,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T12:31:30.000Z","msg":"如果你開廿七八度都凍到要著長衫長褲<br />\n做「咁多運動同控制飲食」都一樣咁病法既話<br />\n你本身個身體應該都幾廢下<br />\n唔好諗住靠自己做運動控制飲食搞掂<br />\n我係你就睇醫生 信既搵到堅既就睇中醫<br />\n唔信既就搵西醫治標"},{"pid":"d490f38b7fb39ef8cbdb26748d5c9e6ede7aa358","tid":1676400,"uid":149012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"朋友話要食多啲補品，比如係飲雞湯果啲，食下維他命Ｃ<br />\n同你一樣病咗差唔多４個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未試過身體去到咁差<br />\n諗緊睇唔睇中醫斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}